    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Sensors and Data AI Assistant\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you solve the mystery scenarios and determine what sensors to use. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n*Request Data Types*: Determine what type of data needs be collected in this scenario.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> I want to measure how loud the highway is throughout the day. What kind of data should I collect?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Ask About Sensors*: Ask about which sensors might help collect the type of data they need to collect.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> I want to collect location data to track how far the flock of geese in my neighborhood travel in a day. What kind of sensor should I use?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Propose Solutions*: Share your ideas for solving the problem, and ask the chatbot if your solution is feasible based on the data.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> Would it make sense to use a weight sensor to determine when to restock the vending machine?\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Keep Learning*: Feel free to ask \"why\" or \"how\" questions to deepen your understanding of sensors and data.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> Can you give me more information on how radar works?\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n",
    "aichat_settings": {
      "initialCustomizations": {
